Achievements.Name: Follow the Light
Achievements.Description: Take a night course of light education.

Achievements.Name: Nordic Walking
Achievements.Description: Take a walk through the logging area, meet one of the quirky locals.

Achievements.Name: Under a Thin Layer of Skin
Park Ranger
Achievements.Description: Enjoy the sounds and sights of Elderwood National Park.

Achievements.Name: Child of the Elder God
Achievements.Description: Have a rock'n'roll moment without dropping to a low health state.

Achievements.Name: Perchance to Dream
Achievements.Description: Take a moment to reflect on past events.

Achievements.Name: Drink 'Em Both Up
Achievements.Description: Put de lime in de coconut twice.

Achievements.Name: Gatekeeper
Achievements.Description: Cut the power to the transformer yard.

Achievements.Name: Departure
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on Normal difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Hardboiled Writer
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on Hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Alan, Wake Up
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on Nightmare difficulty.

Achievements.Name: They're Heeeeeere!
Achievements.Description: Inanimate objects shouldn't move of their own accord. Put a stop to this affront, oh, say, 20 times.

Achievements.Name: Taken Season
Achievements.Description: Defeat 50 Taken with the hunting rifle.

Achievements.Name: It's Not Just a Typewriter Brand
What Light Through Yonder Window
Achievements.Description: Defeat 50 Taken with the flaregun, the way Shakespeare intended.

Achievements.Name: Come One, Come All
Achievements.Description: Kill four Taken with a single shot from the flaregun.

Achievements.Name: Sound and Fury
Achievements.Description: Kill four Taken with a single flashbang.

Achievements.Name: Two For the Price of One
Achievements.Description: Kill two Taken with a single shotgun blast.

Achievements.Name: Meet the Deadline
Achievements.Description: In ''Mirror Peak,'' make it from the Coal Mine Museum to Cauldron Lake in 30 minutes.

Achievements.Name: An Idyllic Small Town
Achievements.Description: Make it through ''Night Life in Bright Falls'' in one go without dying or restarting even once.

Achievements.Name: Gunless Wonder
Achievements.Description: Make it to Cauldron Lake without firing a single shot in ''On the Road to Cauldron Lake.''

Achievements.Name: Every Nook and Cranny
Achievements.Description: Discover all of the hidden chests.

Achievements.Name: Picking Up After Yourself
Achievements.Description: Find all of the manuscript pages in Normal mode.

Achievements.Name: Collector's Edition
Achievements.Description: Find all of the manuscript pages in the game, including the ones in Nightmare mode.

Achievements.Name: KBF-FM
Achievements.Description: Listen to all of the radio shows.

Achievements.Name: Bright Falls Aficionado
Achievements.Description: Absorb every bit of local history and culture.
